description: Hugo Boss AG, together with its subsidiaries, develops, markets, and distributes clothes, shoes, and accessories for men and women worldwide. It offers business, casual, athleisure, and evening wear; shoes and accessories; and licensed products, including fragrances, eyewear, and watches, as well as children's fashion products. The company markets and sells its products under the BOSS and HUGO brand names through online stores, freestanding stores, shop-in-shops, and factory outlets. As of December 31, 2021, it operated 1,228 retail points of sale. The company was founded in 1924 and is headquartered in Metzingen, Germany.
